[
    {
        "text": "Under a bright sun,...",
        "startTime": 1825,
        "endTime": 2980,
        "slowStartTime": 2888,
        "slowEndTime": 4695
    },
    {
        "text": "...skiers and snowboarders are enjoying the kind of powder you might find in the Alps,...",
        "startTime": 3071,
        "endTime": 7913,
        "slowStartTime": 4757,
        "slowEndTime": 12095
    },
    {
        "text": "...but this isn't Europe.",
        "startTime": 9589,
        "endTime": 10961,
        "slowStartTime": 14533,
        "slowEndTime": 16666
    },
    {
        "text": "This is Lesotho in southern Africa.",
        "startTime": 11302,
        "endTime": 13876,
        "slowStartTime": 17103,
        "slowEndTime": 21039
    },
    {
        "text": "My name is Ramokotjo Hope.",
        "startTime": 14173,
        "endTime": 15519,
        "slowStartTime": 21409,
        "slowEndTime": 23503
    },
    {
        "text": "I'm a snowboarding and a skiing instructor, and this is my playground.",
        "startTime": 16116,
        "endTime": 19876,
        "slowStartTime": 24324,
        "slowEndTime": 30039
    },
    {
        "text": "Though a vacation in Africa might typically conjure images of palm-fringed beaches...",
        "startTime": 21841,
        "endTime": 25836,
        "slowStartTime": 32912,
        "slowEndTime": 38979
    },
    {
        "text": "...or herds of wildebeests migrating across the savannah,...",
        "startTime": 25909,
        "endTime": 28761,
        "slowStartTime": 39014,
        "slowEndTime": 43366
    },
    {
        "text": "...the continent also has five mountain ranges with enough seasonal snow...",
        "startTime": 29091,
        "endTime": 33272,
        "slowStartTime": 43786,
        "slowEndTime": 50133
    },
    {
        "text": "...to create the potential for slopes.",
        "startTime": 33347,
        "endTime": 35620,
        "slowStartTime": 50171,
        "slowEndTime": 53655
    },
    {
        "text": "One resort can be found in Lesotho,...",
        "startTime": 37339,
        "endTime": 39395,
        "slowStartTime": 56159,
        "slowEndTime": 59318
    },
    {
        "text": "...the enclaved kingdom tucked into South Africa's Drakensberg mountain range.",
        "startTime": 39563,
        "endTime": 43831,
        "slowStartTime": 59495,
        "slowEndTime": 65971
    },
    {
        "text": "Hope says most people don't think of Africa for a ski holiday,...",
        "startTime": 45918,
        "endTime": 48935,
        "slowStartTime": 69027,
        "slowEndTime": 73627
    },
    {
        "text": "...but are amazed at what they find.",
        "startTime": 49149,
        "endTime": 51329,
        "slowStartTime": 73873,
        "slowEndTime": 77218
    },
    {
        "text": "This isn't much, but people come in and have a whole lot of fun.",
        "startTime": 51823,
        "endTime": 56843,
        "slowStartTime": 77884,
        "slowEndTime": 85490
    },
    {
        "text": "Let alone, for me as a local, I don't have to fly out of here.",
        "startTime": 57240,
        "endTime": 62515,
        "slowStartTime": 86010,
        "slowEndTime": 93998
    },
    {
        "text": "I got a vacation right here.",
        "startTime": 63157,
        "endTime": 64466,
        "slowStartTime": 94886,
        "slowEndTime": 96924
    }
